<ApplicationLayout
  title="Alfa Laval NX 418 Decanter | Sludge Thickening Centrifuge"
  description="Alfa Laval NX-418 B31-G two-phase decanter centrifuge: 110 GPM, 3,150 Gs, 4,000 RPM. Dolphin Centrifuge supplies NX-418 sales, rebuilds, and parts — Warren, MI."
