  <article class="prose-dolphin max-w-none">

    <!-- NX 418 Two-Phase Overview -->
    <h2 id="nx418-two-phase">Alfa Laval NX 418 B31-G Two-Phase Decanter Centrifuge</h2>
    <p>
      The Alfa Laval NX 418 <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/">Decanter Centrifuge</a> is a horizontal de-sludging centrifuge built for the two-phase separation of <strong>wastewater</strong>, <strong>crude oil tank bottoms</strong>, municipal <strong>sludge-thickening</strong>, industrial sludge dewatering, <strong>paint sludge handling</strong>, etc.
    </p>
    <p>
      With a 20 HP Motor, the NX 418 decanter has a <strong>bowl RPM of 4,000</strong> and can process <strong>110 GPM of water with light sludge</strong>.
    </p>

    <!-- Applications -->
    <h2 id="applications">Applications</h2>
    <p>The Alfa Laval NX-418 Decanter is used for the following applications.</p>
    <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm list-none !pl-0">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/ethanol-extraction-centrifuges-technical-comparison/">Ethanol Extraction Centrifuge</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/waste-oil-centrifuge/">Waste Oil De-sludging</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/crude-oil-centrifuge/">Crude Oil Tank Bottom Sludge</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/">Municipal Wastewater</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/pyrolysis-oil-centrifuge/">Pyrolysis Sludge Separation</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/liquid-humus-centrifuge/">Liquid Humus Fertilizer</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/">Sludge Thickening &amp; Dewatering</a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <span>Paint Sludge Handling</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

