    <!-- Specifications Two-Phase -->
    <h2 id="specifications-two-phase">Specifications</h2>
    <p>The following are the technical specifications for the Alfa Laval NX 418 B31-G two-phase decanter centrifuge.</p>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <table>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-semibold w-1/2">Model Type</td>
            <td class="font-mono font-bold">Alfa Laval NX 418 B31-G Decanter Centrifuge</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-semibold">Rated Capacity</td>
            <td class="font-mono font-bold">110 GPM on Water Sludge Thickening</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-semibold">Auger Differential Speed</td>
            <td class="font-mono">1 ~ 50 RPM</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-semibold">Drive Motor Power</td>
            <td class="font-mono">20 HP</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="font-semibold">GearBox Ratio</td>
            <td class="font-mono">1 : 159 (2.5 kN-M)</td>
          </tr>
