    <!-- UVNX 418 Three-Phase -->
    <h2 id="uvnx418">Alfa Laval UVNX 418 B-11 Three-Phase Decanter Centrifuge (Tricanter)</h2>
    <p>
      The Alfa Laval UVNX 418 Decanter is a <a href="/three-phase-decanter/">three-phase decanter</a> centrifuge specially built for the three-phase separation of fish oil, olive oil, animal fat-rendering, etc.
    </p>
    <p>
      With a 25 HP Motor, the UVNX 418 decanter centrifuge has a bowl RPM of 4,000 and can process 70 GPM of Fish Oil and Meal Separation.
    </p>
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-nx-418-decanter-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-NX418-Decaner-C1D2-for-Hemp-Ethanol-Processing-600.webp"
